{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4855c92c9a","title":"中央转发北京市委关于摧毁一贯道的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62b92d00ce","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"4855c92c9a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40d305fab3","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委关于摧毁一贯道的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45e7910515","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转所属分局，省委，大中市委，区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb364b03fe","type":"paragraph","text":"关于摧毁一贯道，北京的经验是很成功的。一是长期侦察布置，不是仓促举行；二是临事向群众宣传，孤立道首；三是布置展览会；四是退道款；五是与反迷信分开。以上各项可作各地参考。一贯道在全国有几百万被欺骗的落后群众，各省凡有大批一贯道存在的地方，党对这个问题的处理必须采取慎重和适当的态度","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef72c6e58d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0e45c0cf7","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4855c92c9a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":146,"end":146}}}},"__N_SSG":true}